    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering a broad torque curve and 320 hp. The G96 6-speed manual transaxle offers precise shift gates, paired with a chassis that retains its factory-spec composure through MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear suspension. This example has been properly sorted with an IMS bearing retrofit and a recent borescope inspection to ensure cylinder wall integrity. The braking system utilizes four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors for exceptional thermal management. While exhibiting minor aesthetic wear consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, its mechanical vitals are robust, making it an ideal candidate for the purist seeking an analog rear-engine experience.",
